x=r_xe^{j\alpha}
y=r_ye^{j\beta}
\frac{y}{x}=\frac{1+{|y|}^2}{1+{|y|}^2}
\Rightarrow \frac{r_ye^{j\beta}}{r_xe^{j\alpha}}=\frac{1+{r_y}^2}{1+{r_x^2}}
\alpha=\beta
r_x-r_y+r_xr_y(r_y-r_x)=0 
\Rightarrow r_x=r_y \text{ or }r_xr_y=1 
\text{In other words }r_xr_ye^{j\alpha -j\beta}=1 \text{ or } x\bar{y}=1  
